WEBVTT

00:05.376 --> 00:08.509
THE GOOD DOCTOR HAS JUST
PERFORMED A HEMISPHERECTOMY

00:08.509 --> 00:10.611
TO REMOVE THE DISEASED HALF
OF THE BRAIN.

00:10.611 --> 00:12.683
THIS IS JOHNNY'S LEFT
HEMISPHERE,

00:12.683 --> 00:15.015
THE SIDE THAT CONTAINS
HIS LANGUAGE CENTER.

00:15.015 --> 00:18.619
IT'S ALSO THE HALF OF HIS BRAIN
WE HAD TO TAKE OUT.

00:18.619 --> 00:20.721
AMAZINGLY,
SPEECH AND OTHER FUNCTIONS

00:20.721 --> 00:23.094
ONCE CONTROLLED
BY THE LEFT HEMISPHERE

00:23.094 --> 00:25.456
WILL EVENTUALLY DEVELOP
IN THE RIGHT.

00:25.456 --> 00:28.099
HEMISPHERECTOMIES
NOT ONLY SAVE LIVES,

00:28.099 --> 00:30.701
THEY ALSO SHOW US
THAT TO BE FULLY HUMAN

00:30.701 --> 00:32.403
ONLY TAKES HALF A BRAIN,

00:32.403 --> 00:35.136
WHICH SOME OF YOU DEMONSTRATE
ON A DAILY BASIS.

00:35.136 --> 00:36.707
[ LAUGHTER ]
AS FOR THE REST OF YOU,

00:36.707 --> 00:39.270
DOES THAT MEAN YOU HAVE
A LOT MORE BRAIN POWER

00:39.270 --> 00:40.641
THAN YOU REALLY NEED?

00:40.641 --> 00:44.215
OR DOES IT MEAN
THAT YOU HAVE VAST AMOUNTS

00:44.215 --> 00:47.818
OF UNREALIZED POTENTIAL?

00:51.122 --> 00:53.424
TELL ME YOU'RE NOT WEARING
THAT RATTY COAT AND SCARF.

00:53.424 --> 00:54.625
WHY WOULDN'T I?

00:54.625 --> 00:56.127
WELL, FOR ONE THING,
IT'S 60 DEGREES OUT.

00:56.127 --> 00:57.588
THAT'S GOT
NOTHING TO DO WITH IT.

00:57.588 --> 00:59.360
MORE IMPORTANTLY,
THERE ARE GONNA BE

00:59.360 --> 01:01.632
A LOT OF DEEP POCKETS
AT THIS EVENT TONIGHT, DANIEL,

01:01.632 --> 01:03.094
AND, YOU KNOW,

01:03.094 --> 01:04.495
FACULTY ENDOWMENTS
DON'T FUND THEMSELVES.

01:04.495 --> 01:06.297
IT'S A FUNDRAISER
FOR PARKINSON'S RESEARCH,

01:06.297 --> 01:08.068
NOT YOUR OWN
PERSONAL SLUSH FUND.

01:08.068 --> 01:10.501
IF SOMEBODY'S GONNA WRITE ONE
CHECK, MAYBE THEY'LL WRITE TWO.

01:10.501 --> 01:13.073
UNBELIEVABLE.
WELL, WOULD IT KILL YOU
TO WEAR A TIE?

01:13.073 --> 01:14.745
WHAT, AND CUT OFF
THE OXYGEN TO MY BRAIN

01:14.745 --> 01:16.407
JUST TO KISS UP
TO SOME FAT CATS?

01:16.407 --> 01:17.408
NO, THANK YOU.

01:17.408 --> 01:19.550
HEY, PEOPLE,
GET A ROOM.

01:19.550 --> 01:20.511
LEWICKI?

01:22.213 --> 01:24.755
HEY, DOC, UH --
SHOULDN'T YOU
BE GRADING MIDTERMS?

01:24.755 --> 01:28.159
UH, I WAS JUST...
TAKING A LITTLE BREAK.

01:29.089 --> 01:30.221
THIS IS EVA.

01:30.221 --> 01:32.223
SO, YOU'RE DR. PIERCE.

01:32.223 --> 01:34.495
FROM WHAT MAX TOLD ME,
I THOUGHT YOU'D BE --

01:34.495 --> 01:35.626
BETTER DRESSED?

01:35.626 --> 01:37.128
OLDER.

01:37.128 --> 01:39.500
DOC, I-I WAS HOPING
YOU COULD TALK TO EVA

01:39.500 --> 01:41.372
ABOUT
THE EXTENSION SCHOOL.

01:41.372 --> 01:44.375
AS RIVETING AS THAT SOUNDS,
DEAN HALEY AND I ARE ON OUR WAY

01:44.375 --> 01:47.107
TO HEAR ONE OF THE GREATEST
VIOLINISTS IN THE WORLD.

01:47.107 --> 01:48.108
CAN'T BE LATE.

01:51.382 --> 01:52.743
[ CHUCKLES ]

01:52.743 --> 01:56.747
[ MID-TEMPO VIOLIN MUSIC
PLAYING ]

02:07.798 --> 02:09.830
[ OFF-KEY NOTES PLAY ]

02:12.903 --> 02:15.306
[ AUDIENCE MURMURING ]

02:16.807 --> 02:18.469
[ GRUNTS ]

02:21.272 --> 02:22.373
[ GRUNTING ]

02:22.373 --> 02:24.775
SOMEBODY CALL
AN AMBULANCE.

02:33.153 --> 02:35.856
[ GROANS ]
[ DEVICE BEEPS ]

02:35.856 --> 02:37.288
[ PANTING ]

02:37.288 --> 02:38.289
BREATHE.

02:45.566 --> 02:47.498
Paul:
DANIEL, WHAT HAPPENED TO HIM?

02:47.498 --> 02:48.939
I'M NOT SURE.

02:48.939 --> 02:50.671
IT COULD HAVE BEEN SIDE EFFECTS
FROM HIS DBS.

02:50.671 --> 02:52.343
DBS?
DEEP BRAIN STIMULATOR.

02:52.343 --> 02:54.475
HE HAS ELECTRODES IMPLANTED
IN HIS BRAIN

02:54.475 --> 02:56.647
TO HELP RELIEVE
HIS PARKINSON'S SYMPTOMS.

02:56.647 --> 02:59.380
IT'S POWERED BY A BATTERY PACK
IN HIS CHEST.

02:59.380 --> 03:00.681
I TURNED IT OFF.

03:00.681 --> 03:01.782
PARKINSON'S?
HE'S SO YOUNG.
I KNOW.

03:01.782 --> 03:04.255
10% OF THE CASES
ARE UNDER 40.

03:04.255 --> 03:05.616
AND HOW DID YOU KNOW
ABOUT THAT --

03:05.616 --> 03:07.488
WELL, THERE WAS AN ARTICLE
IN THE ARTS SECTION

03:07.488 --> 03:08.959
ABOUT SARIO
A FEW MONTHS AGO.

03:08.959 --> 03:10.721
AND HE HAD TO RETIRE
BECAUSE OF HIS PARKINSON'S,

03:10.721 --> 03:12.863
AND THEN ONCE HIS DBS WAS
IMPLANTED, HE COULD PLAY AGAIN.

03:12.863 --> 03:14.225
WOW.
Sario: MY VIOLIN.

03:14.225 --> 03:15.526
MY VIOLIN!
WHERE IS MY VIOLIN?

03:15.526 --> 03:16.727
I'LL -- I'LL MAKE SURE
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

03:16.727 --> 03:18.329
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

03:18.329 --> 03:20.801
PLEASE COME TO THE HOSPITAL
WITH ME.

03:20.801 --> 03:22.333
I THINK IT'S BEST
WE CALL YOUR OWN DOCTOR.

03:22.333 --> 03:23.834
I WANT FOR YOU TO TELL HIM
WHAT HAPPENED.

03:23.834 --> 03:26.577
ALL RIGHT.

03:26.577 --> 03:27.978
THE SETTINGS
ARE MUCH TOO HIGH.

03:27.978 --> 03:28.979
HOW COULD THAT HAPPEN?

03:28.979 --> 03:30.481
I DON'T KNOW.

03:30.481 --> 03:31.712
BUT IT'S A GOOD THING
YOU WERE THERE,

03:31.712 --> 03:33.213
OR IT MIGHT HAVE BEEN
MUCH WORSE.

03:33.213 --> 03:35.486
DR. VETTER, YOU KNOW,
TOMORROW NIGHT,

03:35.486 --> 03:37.748
I GONNA PLAY
WITH THE SYMPHONY, SO...

03:37.748 --> 03:39.890
I NEED YOU TO TURN MY DBS
BACK ON.

03:39.890 --> 03:41.952
I DON'T THINK
WE CAN TAKE THAT RISK.

03:41.952 --> 03:43.354
NO, I DON'T CARE.

03:43.354 --> 03:44.955
IF MY HANDS
DON'T STOP SHAKING,

03:44.955 --> 03:46.757
HOW CAN I PLAY?
Tess:
I CAME AS SOON AS I HEARD.

03:46.757 --> 03:48.429
HANG ON A MINUTE,
TESS.

03:48.429 --> 03:50.461
UH, TESS WILLIAMS
FROM OsciDyne,

03:50.461 --> 03:53.233
THE COMPANY
THAT MAKES SARIO'S DBS.

03:53.233 --> 03:54.805
LET ME TELL HER
WHAT'S GOING ON,

03:54.805 --> 03:57.408
AND THEN WE'LL TALK ABOUT
HOW TO GET YOU PERFORMING AGAIN.

03:59.470 --> 04:00.741
HIS LEVELS SURGE.

04:00.741 --> 04:02.643
IT'S JUST LIKE THE CASES
I TOLD YOU ABOUT

04:02.643 --> 04:04.014
AT THE CONFERENCE
IN MIAMI.

04:04.014 --> 04:06.016
WHAT, THERE WERE OTHER INCIDENTS
LIKE SARIO'S?

04:06.016 --> 04:07.418
I'M SORRY.
WHO ARE YOU?

04:07.418 --> 04:08.779
TESS WILLIAMS,
DR. DANIEL PIERCE,

04:08.779 --> 04:10.481
THE MAN
WHO SAVED SARIO'S LIFE.

04:10.481 --> 04:12.252
Dr. Vetter:
OVER THE PAST FEW MONTHS,

04:12.252 --> 04:14.555
EIGHT PATIENTS FITTED WITH
THE OsciDyne 5.0 MODEL

04:14.555 --> 04:15.786
HAVE REPORTED MALFUNCTIONS.

04:15.786 --> 04:17.388
THESE PEOPLE
HAD SEIZURES, TOO?

04:17.388 --> 04:19.790
SOME DID. OTHERS LOCKED UP
OR COULDN'T SPEAK.

04:19.790 --> 04:21.632
LUCKILY,
NOBODY DIED.

04:21.632 --> 04:23.263
WELL, OBVIOUSLY,
THE 5.0 IS FLAWED.

04:23.263 --> 04:24.935
WELL, ACTUALLY,
IT'S NOT OBVIOUS AT ALL.

04:24.935 --> 04:26.867
OUR TECHNICIANS
HAVEN'T FOUND ANY PROBLEMS

04:26.867 --> 04:27.938
WITH THE RECOVERED UNIT.

04:27.938 --> 04:29.370
OF COURSE THEY HAVEN'T.

04:29.370 --> 04:31.402
YOUR COMPANY
PAYS THEIR SALARIES.

04:31.402 --> 04:35.476
OUR POSITION IS THAT THE 5.0
IS FUNCTIONING PROPERLY.

04:35.476 --> 04:38.879
IF IT'S FUNCTIONING PROPERLY,
WHY IS SARIO LYING IN THAT BED?

04:38.879 --> 04:40.581
I KNOW YOU'RE IN
A TOUGH SPOT, TESS,

04:40.581 --> 04:42.353
BUT I AM TAKING
SARIO'S DEVICE OUT,

04:42.353 --> 04:44.585
AND I'M GONNA RECOMMEND
THAT ALL MY PATIENTS

04:44.585 --> 04:46.717
FITTED WITH THESE UNITS
HAVE THEM REMOVED.

04:46.717 --> 04:48.619
OsciDyne
NEEDS TO COVER THE COSTS.

04:48.619 --> 04:50.421
I'M SORRY, RANDALL.
I DON'T SEE THAT HAPPENING.

04:50.421 --> 04:52.292
Dr. Vetter: AND WHAT IF
ONE OF MY OTHER PATIENTS,

04:52.292 --> 04:54.925
OR, GOD FORBID, MY WIFE,
ENDS UP IN THE HOSPITAL?

04:54.925 --> 04:56.967
I'M TAKING THEM OUT.

04:56.967 --> 04:58.399
I'M SORRY, YOUR WIFE?

04:58.399 --> 04:59.830
SHE HAS DBS
FOR ESSENTIAL TREMOR.

04:59.830 --> 05:02.603
AND HOW IS SHE GONNA FEEL
WHEN YOU REMOVE HER UNIT

05:02.603 --> 05:04.575
AND HER HANDS
START SHAKING AGAIN?

05:04.575 --> 05:08.339
SHE'LL BE UPSET,
BUT AT LEAST SHE'LL BE ALIVE.

05:10.811 --> 05:12.643
[ SIGHS ]

05:12.643 --> 05:17.388
Woman: INTRODUCING OsciDyne's
REVOLUTIONARY DBS 5.0,

05:17.388 --> 05:19.590
THE MOST ADVANCED
AND AFFORDABLE

05:19.590 --> 05:21.952
DEEP BRAIN STIMULATOR
ON THE MARKET.

05:21.952 --> 05:24.855
THE BATTERY PACK AND
COMPUTER-CONTROLLED STIMULATOR

05:24.855 --> 05:27.598
ARE IMPLANTED IN A MINIMALLY
INVASIVE PROCEDURE.

05:27.598 --> 05:29.329
INSULATED TUNGSTEN
EXTENSION WIRES

05:29.329 --> 05:30.831
TRAVEL FROM THE STIMULATOR
TO THE ELECTRODES,

05:30.831 --> 05:33.964
WHICH TARGET SPECIFIC REGIONS
OF THE BRAIN

05:33.964 --> 05:36.006
DEPENDING ON THE DIAGNOSIS
AND SYMPTOMS.

05:36.006 --> 05:39.009
TODAY, THE 5.0 TREATS
PARKINSON'S, DYSTONIA,

05:39.009 --> 05:41.011
ESSENTIAL TREMOR,
AND TOURETTE'S.

05:41.011 --> 05:42.673
OUR NEXT-GENERATION DBS

05:42.673 --> 05:45.546
WILL TREAT ALZHEIMER'S,
OBESITY, AND MORE.

05:45.546 --> 05:48.449
[ SCOFFS ] ARE YOU --
ARE YOU LISTENING TO THIS?

05:48.449 --> 05:49.620
OBESITY.

05:49.620 --> 05:50.821
I MEAN,
I-I-IF PEOPLE ARE FAT,

05:50.821 --> 05:52.653
THEY SHOULD STOP
STUFFING THEIR FACES

05:52.653 --> 05:54.755
WITH CHEESEBURGERS AND CUPCAKES,
NOT -- NOT GET BRAIN SURGERY.

05:54.755 --> 05:56.026
WHAT, SO,
IT DOESN'T WORK?

05:56.026 --> 05:57.388
IT [SIGHS]

05:57.388 --> 05:58.759
IT'S A MIRACLE
FOR SOME PEOPLE,

05:58.759 --> 06:00.661
BUT OsciDyne's MODEL
IS CLEARLY DEFECTIVE.

06:00.661 --> 06:03.033
AND THEY'RE MAKING
THESE WILDLY EXAGGERATED CLAIMS

06:03.033 --> 06:04.535
TO LINE THEIR POCKETS

06:04.535 --> 06:06.036
AT THE EXPENSE
OF VULNERABLE PATIENTS.

06:06.036 --> 06:07.898
OKAY, SO, WHAT EXACTLY
DO YOU WANT ME TO DO?

06:07.898 --> 06:09.570
HELP ME INVESTIGATE
OsciDyne.

06:09.570 --> 06:11.802
IF ANYTHING, THIS SOUNDS LIKE
A PRODUCT-LIABILITY ISSUE.

06:11.802 --> 06:13.504
YOU SHOULD GO TO THE FDA.

06:13.504 --> 06:14.905
OH, THE AGENCY THAT'S ALREADY
APPROVED THE DEVICE?

06:14.905 --> 06:16.477
YEAH, I'M SURE
THEY'LL GET RIGHT ON IT.

06:16.477 --> 06:18.078
Donnie: HE'S RIGHT.

06:18.078 --> 06:20.911
WE ALL KNOW THE FDA IS IN BED
WITH THE BIOTECH INDUSTRY.

06:20.911 --> 06:23.784
[ Strained ]
WE'RE REOPENING THE CHAN CASE.

06:23.784 --> 06:26.717
OH, NO.
I NEED YOU TO DO
NEW INTERVIEWS.

06:26.717 --> 06:29.059
WELL, DANIEL,
AS YOU CAN SEE,

06:29.059 --> 06:31.722
NOW I CAN'T HELP YOU
EVEN IF I WANTED TO.

06:31.722 --> 06:32.623
THANKS, DON.

06:38.398 --> 06:40.431
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

06:41.502 --> 06:43.073
I THINK WE MIGHT HAVE
A CASE.

06:43.073 --> 06:45.135
"WE"? WHAT --
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

06:45.135 --> 06:46.777
I DID SOME DIGGING.

06:46.777 --> 06:49.880
OsciDyne IS LEVERAGED
UP TO THEIR ELECTRODES.

06:49.880 --> 06:51.942
IF THEY ADMIT
THIS DBS THING IS DEFECTIVE,

06:51.942 --> 06:53.043
IT COULD BANKRUPT THEM.

06:54.414 --> 06:56.086
YOU THINK
THERE'S A COVER-UP?

06:56.086 --> 06:57.918
NOT EASY TO PROVE,
BUT I'M WILLING TO TRY.

06:57.918 --> 07:00.050
[ CHUCKLES ]
WHAT'S -- WHAT'S YOUR ANGLE?

07:00.050 --> 07:01.492
I DON'T HAVE AN ANGLE.

07:01.492 --> 07:02.793
IT'S MY JOB
TO PROTECT THE PUBLIC.

07:02.793 --> 07:04.455
SO, WHY DO YOU NEED ME?

07:04.455 --> 07:06.657
I HAVE A LAW DEGREE,
NOT A PhD IN BRAIN SCIENCE.

07:06.657 --> 07:07.928
I GO DOWN THERE ON MY OWN,

07:07.928 --> 07:09.800
THEIR EXPERTS
WILL TRY AND SNOW ME

07:09.800 --> 07:11.902
WITH A BUNCH OF
NEUROLOGICAL MUMBO-JUMBO.

07:11.902 --> 07:14.064
I ALREADY CALLED THE DOCTOR
WHO FILED THE COMPLAINT --

07:14.064 --> 07:15.566
VETTER.

07:15.566 --> 07:16.937
WE NEED TO GET HIS STATEMENT
ON THE RECORD.

07:16.937 --> 07:18.809
HE SAID HE'LL MEET US
AT HIS HOUSE IN AN HOUR.

07:18.809 --> 07:19.770
LET'S DO THIS, PARTNER.

07:19.770 --> 07:20.641
[ LAUGHS NERVOUSLY ]

07:20.641 --> 07:22.042
JUST WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

07:22.042 --> 07:24.915
IN THE SHORT, UNPLEASANT TIME
THAT I HAVE KNOWN YOU,

07:24.915 --> 07:27.518
YOU'VE HUMILIATED ME
ON THE WITNESS STAND,

07:27.518 --> 07:28.819
KICKED ME OFF
AN INVESTIGATION,

07:28.819 --> 07:30.681
UNDERMINED MY FRIENDSHIP
WITH YOUR EX-WIFE,

07:30.681 --> 07:32.583
AND NOW, SUDDENLY,
WE'RE PARTNERS?
OKAY.

07:32.583 --> 07:35.125
I GET IT. WE BOTH KNOW THERE'S
AN ELEPHANT IN THE ROOM.

07:35.125 --> 07:39.129
LET'S CLEAR THE AIR.
IF YOU THINK THAT YOU AND I ARE
GONNA TALK ABOUT KATE AGAIN --

07:39.129 --> 07:41.592
WHOA, BUDDY...
I'M TALKING BASEBALL.

07:41.592 --> 07:42.963
WHAT?

07:42.963 --> 07:45.596
YOU LIKE THE CUBBIES,
AND I'M A WHITE SOX GUY,

07:45.596 --> 07:47.838
SO WE'LL JUST TALK ABOUT
THE BULLS.

07:50.871 --> 07:53.974
"SURE THING, DONNIE.
LET'S GO GET THEM."

08:03.784 --> 08:06.617
RYAN, ASSISTANT U.S. ATTORNEY.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

08:06.617 --> 08:08.058
IT'S REAL MESSY
INSIDE.

08:08.058 --> 08:09.760
WHAT THE HELL
HAPPENED?

08:09.760 --> 08:11.922
TWO VICTIMS,
ONE'S DEAD -- A DOCTOR.

08:11.922 --> 08:13.824
SOMEBODY
SMASHED HIS HEAD IN.

08:21.231 --> 08:24.234
SO WHOEVER YOU NEED TO TALK TO
TO GET ME THAT, OKAY?
HEY.

08:24.234 --> 08:25.906
I GOT YOUR MESSAGE.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

08:25.906 --> 08:27.908
DOG-WALKER CALLED IN A 911
AT 8:52 A.M.

08:27.908 --> 08:29.179
POLICE CAME IN
AND FOUND

08:29.179 --> 08:31.011
DR. VETTER AND HIS WIFE
ON THE FLOOR,

08:31.011 --> 08:33.784
BOTH WITH
MASSIVE HEAD WOUNDS.
HE WAS ALREADY DEAD.

08:33.784 --> 08:35.215
SHE WAS ALIVE -- BARELY.

08:35.215 --> 08:37.117
DO THE COPS HAVE
A THEORY?

08:37.117 --> 08:39.519
"HOME INVASION
THAT WENT WRONG."
SURE. AT THE SAME TIME

08:39.519 --> 08:41.852
THAT VETTER STARTS TO COMPLAIN
ABOUT THE 5.0,

08:41.852 --> 08:43.924
HE'S KILLED IN A ROBBERY WHERE
APPARENTLY NOTHING WAS STOLEN.

08:43.924 --> 08:45.525
WHAT MAKES MORE SENSE

08:45.525 --> 08:48.629
IS OsciDyne SENT SOMEBODY
OVER HERE TO SHUT HIM UP.

08:48.629 --> 08:52.062
OKAY, WHAT THE HELL ARE THE TWO
OF YOU DOING HERE, ANYWAY?

08:52.062 --> 08:54.004
WE'RE WORKING
THE PRODUCT-LIABILITY CASE

08:54.004 --> 08:55.666
THAT YOU TURNED DOWN
YESTERDAY.

08:55.666 --> 08:57.007
OH. TOGETHER?

08:57.007 --> 08:58.669
WHAT?

08:58.669 --> 09:00.540
WERE WE SUPPOSED TO ASK
YOUR PERMISSION FIRST?

09:00.540 --> 09:02.913
WE SHOULD GO TO THE HOSPITAL,
SEE WHAT THE WIFE CAN TELL US.

09:10.220 --> 09:13.123
YEAH, THANKS.
THANK YOU.

09:13.123 --> 09:15.726
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

09:15.726 --> 09:17.087
[ SIGHS ]

09:17.087 --> 09:19.690
HER EYES ARE OPEN,
BUT SHE'S UNRESPONSIVE.

09:19.690 --> 09:20.861
WHAT, SO,
SHE'S IN A COMA?

09:20.861 --> 09:22.332
NO, NOT EXACTLY.

09:22.332 --> 09:24.094
IT'S WHAT'S KNOWN AS
A MINIMALLY CONSCIOUS STATE.

09:24.094 --> 09:25.766
WELL, IS SHE
GONNA WAKE UP?

09:25.766 --> 09:26.967
THERE'S NOT MUCH
THE DOCTORS CAN DO.

09:26.967 --> 09:28.699
[ SIGHS ]

09:28.699 --> 09:29.840
IAN.

09:29.840 --> 09:31.101
HI.

09:31.101 --> 09:33.704
UH, AGENT MORETTI.
I'M WITH THE FBI.

09:33.704 --> 09:35.676
LISTEN, CAN YOU
THINK OF ANY REASON

09:35.676 --> 09:38.849
THAT SOMEONE MIGHT HAVE
WANTED TO HURT YOUR PARENTS?

09:38.849 --> 09:40.310
NO.

09:40.310 --> 09:42.953
MY DAD SPENT HIS WHOLE LIFE
HELPING SICK PEOPLE,

09:42.953 --> 09:44.955
AND MY MOM BAKES
BIRTHDAY CAKES

09:44.955 --> 09:47.117
FOR THE GUYS
WHO PICK UP OUR TRASH.

09:47.117 --> 09:48.258
AND THIS IS
WHAT THEY GET.

09:49.960 --> 09:51.591
I'M VERY SORRY.
IS THAT ALL?

09:51.591 --> 09:52.993
'CAUSE I NEED TO GO
CALL MY AUNT.

09:52.993 --> 09:55.796
PLEASE.

09:55.796 --> 09:57.167
[ SIGHS ]

09:57.167 --> 09:59.269
LOOK, I'LL COORDINATE
WITH THE LOCAL COPS,

09:59.269 --> 10:00.771
BUT WE DON'T HAVE MUCH.

10:00.771 --> 10:03.103
I MEAN, NO WEAPON,
NO WITNESSES, NO PRINTS.

10:03.103 --> 10:05.005
WE STILL HAVE
A PRODUCT-LIABILITY CASE.

10:05.005 --> 10:07.107
WHEN WE START DIGGING AROUND,
WE MIGHT BE ABLE

10:07.107 --> 10:09.609
TO NAIL THESE BASTARDS
FOR MURDER, TOO.
LET'S GO.

10:09.609 --> 10:11.281
OKAY, GIVE ME A MINUTE.

10:11.281 --> 10:13.013
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

10:13.013 --> 10:14.645
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

10:14.645 --> 10:16.687
EVERY TIME I TRY TO BRING
DANIEL IN ON A CASE,

10:16.687 --> 10:18.348
YOU SAY
THAT WE DON'T NEED HIM.

10:18.348 --> 10:20.821
NOW THE TWO OF YOU ARE RUNNING
AROUND LIKE STARSKY AND HUTCH?

10:20.821 --> 10:22.622
OsciDyne
MAKES BRAIN DEVICES.

10:22.622 --> 10:24.254
WHO WOULD YOU GET
TO HELP YOU?

10:24.254 --> 10:25.696
OH, CUT THE CRAP,
DONNIE.

10:25.696 --> 10:27.357
EVER SINCE
YOU GOT BACK FROM D.C.,

10:27.357 --> 10:30.901
YOU HAVE BEEN TRYING TO DRIVE
A WEDGE BETWEEN ME AND DANIEL.

10:30.901 --> 10:33.904
NOW, I DON'T KNOW IF THIS
IS PART OF SOME GRAND PLAN

10:33.904 --> 10:36.166
YOU MIGHT HAVE
TO GET US BACK TOGETHER,

10:36.166 --> 10:38.008
BUT IT'S NOT GONNA WORK.

10:38.008 --> 10:40.040
YOU HAVE A HELL
OF AN IMAGINATION.
THEN WHAT IS IT?

10:40.040 --> 10:42.272
YOU WANT YOUR NAME IN THE PAPER?
WHAT'S YOUR ANGLE?

10:42.272 --> 10:44.715
[ SIGHS ] WHY DOES EVERYONE
THINK I HAVE AN ANGLE?

10:44.715 --> 10:46.176
'CAUSE YOU ALWAYS DO?

10:47.377 --> 10:50.350
THERE IS NOTHING WRONG
WITH THE 5.0.

10:50.350 --> 10:53.924
THEN HOW DO YOU EXPLAIN
NINE FAILED UNITS?

10:53.924 --> 10:55.686
WE'VE SOLD
ALMOST 500 OF THEM.

10:55.686 --> 10:57.157
THAT'S
LESS THAN 2%.

10:57.157 --> 10:59.259
I WILL TELL YOU THE SAME THING
WE TOLD THE FDA --

10:59.259 --> 11:00.831
WE HAVE DOUBLE-CHECKED

11:00.831 --> 11:02.262
OUR PRODUCTION
AND DISTRIBUTION PROTOCOLS,

11:02.262 --> 11:04.064
AND WE DIDN'T FIND
A SINGLE PROBLEM.

11:04.064 --> 11:07.097
DID SOMEONE FROM THIS COMPANY
ATTACK DR. VETTER AND HIS WIFE?

11:07.097 --> 11:09.199
YOU'RE ON
A FISHING EXPEDITION.

11:09.199 --> 11:11.441
UNLESS YOU'VE GOT A WARRANT,
THIS CONVERSATION IS OVER.

11:11.441 --> 11:13.243
ACTUALLY,
WE'RE JUST GETTING STARTED.

11:13.243 --> 11:15.445
THE GOVERNMENT'S POSITION
IS THAT IF YOU CANNOT PROVIDE

11:15.445 --> 11:17.207
AN EXPLANATION
FOR THESE PROBLEMS,

11:17.207 --> 11:18.949
WE'RE GOING TO SEEK
AN INJUNCTION

11:18.949 --> 11:20.350
TO STOP ALL SALES
OF THE 5.0.

11:20.350 --> 11:23.183
GOOD LUCK GETTING A JUDGE
TO SIGN OFF ON THAT.

11:23.183 --> 11:24.915
WELL, IF I CAN'T,

11:24.915 --> 11:26.256
I GUESS I'LL JUST HAVE TO
CONVENE A PRESS CONFERENCE

11:26.256 --> 11:28.088
AND EXPLAIN TO THE PUBLIC
HOW OsciDyne

11:28.088 --> 11:29.790
IS IMPEDING
A FEDERAL INVESTIGATION

11:29.790 --> 11:31.391
INTO ONE OF ITS PRODUCTS.

11:31.391 --> 11:33.824
I'M SURE SARIO DONATI WOULD HAVE
SOMETHING TO DAY ABOUT THAT.

11:33.824 --> 11:37.067
WONDER WHAT THAT WOULD DO
TO YOUR STOCK PRICE.

11:38.428 --> 11:39.970
MM.

11:39.970 --> 11:42.302
THERE IS ONE POSSIBILITY
FOR THE FAILURES.

11:42.302 --> 11:44.374
AND WHAT WOULD THAT BE,
MR. SINGH?

11:44.374 --> 11:45.776
IT'S DR. SINGH.

11:45.776 --> 11:48.809
I HOLD A PhD
IN BIOMEDICAL ENGINEERING.

11:48.809 --> 11:50.310
AND I'M A.U.S.A. RYAN,

11:50.310 --> 11:52.943
MAGNA CUM LAUDE IN
NOT WASTING MY TIME ON BULLSHIT.

11:54.044 --> 11:55.846
THERE AREN'T
A LOT OF DOCTORS

11:55.846 --> 11:57.848
WHO KNOW HOW TO USE
THIS TECHNOLOGY,

11:57.848 --> 11:59.850
SO I DESIGNED THE 5.0
FOR PATIENTS

11:59.850 --> 12:01.992
WHO WOULD OTHERWISE
HAVE TO DRIVE HOURS

12:01.992 --> 12:03.253
FOR ROUTINE PROGRAMMING.

12:03.253 --> 12:05.455
NOW THEY CAN USE
WIRELESS TECHNOLOGY

12:05.455 --> 12:08.058
TO LINK THEIR UNITS
TO THEIR HOME COMPUTERS.

12:08.058 --> 12:09.459
THEIR DOCTORS
CAN GO ONLINE

12:09.459 --> 12:11.962
AND MAKE ADJUSTMENTS
TO THE DBS REMOTELY.

12:11.962 --> 12:14.404
SO, IF SOMEONE COULD FIND OUT
THE PATIENT'S ACCESS CODES,

12:14.404 --> 12:16.236
THEY COULD TAMPER
WITH THE SETTINGS.

12:16.236 --> 12:17.737
IT IS POSSIBLE.

12:17.737 --> 12:19.039
AND WHY WOULD ANYONE
DO THAT?

12:19.039 --> 12:21.772
THERE WAS A NEUROSURGEON
WHO WORKED FOR US

12:21.772 --> 12:23.173
AS A CONSULTANT.

12:23.173 --> 12:26.076
ABOUT A YEAR AGO, HE QUIT
AND WENT BACK TO ACADEMIA.

12:26.076 --> 12:28.148
NOT LONG AFTER THAT,

12:28.148 --> 12:30.180
OUR BIGGEST COMPETITOR,
MediVolt,

12:30.180 --> 12:33.223
FUNDED HIS CLINICAL TRIAL
TO THE TUNE OF $4 MILLION.

12:34.424 --> 12:37.027
YOU THINK I'M SOME SORT OF
CORPORATE SPY?

12:37.027 --> 12:38.428
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

12:38.428 --> 12:40.831
WHERE ARE YOU
GETTING THIS?

12:40.831 --> 12:43.894
OH, WAIT, DON'T TELL ME --
ARTHUR SINGH.

12:43.894 --> 12:45.765
[ LAUGHS ]
THAT GUY.

12:45.765 --> 12:47.167
HE'S A COMPLETE EGOMANIAC.

12:47.167 --> 12:48.498
HE IS BLAMING ME

12:48.498 --> 12:50.941
'CAUSE HE'D NEVER ADMIT
TO A FLAW IN HIS DESIGN,

12:50.941 --> 12:53.303
BUT HIS SABOTAGE THEORY
DOESN'T EVEN WORK.

12:53.303 --> 12:55.175
IT SEEMS
PRETTY SIMPLE TO ME.

12:55.175 --> 12:57.177
IF MediVolt
HAD THE ACCESS CODES,

12:57.177 --> 12:59.179
THEY COULD ZAP OsciDyne
PATIENTS.

12:59.179 --> 13:00.780
IT'S NOT THAT EASY.

13:00.780 --> 13:02.913
THE PATIENT NEEDS TO BE
WITHIN ABOUT 50 FEET

13:02.913 --> 13:05.055
OF A COMPUTER
WITH THE 5.0 SOFTWARE.

13:05.055 --> 13:07.988
THAT'S THE ONLY WAY ANYONE
COULD CHANGE THE SETTINGS.

13:07.988 --> 13:09.789
WHEN SARIO
HAD HIS SEIZURE,

13:09.789 --> 13:11.791
HE WAS NOWHERE NEAR
HIS COMPUTER.

13:11.791 --> 13:14.164
THANK YOU FOR YOUR TIME,
DR. BOWEN.

13:14.164 --> 13:15.225
DO YOU HAVE A MINUTE?

13:16.296 --> 13:17.898
IT'S A PROFESSIONAL MATTER.

13:17.898 --> 13:20.530
GO AHEAD.
I GOT TO MAKE A PHONE CALL.

13:20.530 --> 13:22.132
UH...

13:22.132 --> 13:23.533
I READ ALL YOUR BOOKS.

13:23.533 --> 13:27.107
MOST GREAT THINKERS AREN'T
USUALLY SUCH GOOD WRITERS.

13:27.107 --> 13:28.338
HARDLY SEEMS FAIR.

13:28.338 --> 13:30.140
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU?

13:30.140 --> 13:31.842
I'VE BEEN DOING
SOME INTERESTING WORK

13:31.842 --> 13:33.183
USING DBS
TO TREAT DEPRESSION.

13:33.183 --> 13:35.345
I'M GONNA APPLY IT
TO MY NEXT CLINICAL TRIAL,

13:35.345 --> 13:38.088
WHICH WILL TEST DBS AS
A TREATMENT FOR SCHIZOPHRENIA.

13:38.088 --> 13:40.891
[ CHUCKLES ]
THAT WON'T WORK.

13:40.891 --> 13:43.223
ACTUALLY, WE'VE HAD A LOT OF
SUCCESS IN ANIMAL TRIALS.

13:43.223 --> 13:45.025
JUST BECAUSE
YOU'VE BEEN EXPERIMENTING

13:45.025 --> 13:46.957
WITH DOPAMINERGIC TRANSMISSION
IN MICE

13:46.957 --> 13:48.959
DOESN'T MEAN
IT'S GONNA WORK ON PEOPLE.

13:48.959 --> 13:50.300
UNLESS WE TRY,
WE'LL NEVER KNOW.

13:50.300 --> 13:53.563
I WOULD LIKE YOU TO BE
A CONSULTANT FOR MY STUDY.

13:53.563 --> 13:56.366
I ONLY CONSULT ON
INDEPENDENTLY FINANCED STUDIES,

13:56.366 --> 13:58.508
NOT CORPORATE-SPONSORED
MONEY GRABS.

13:58.508 --> 14:00.240
BIG IDEAS
NEED BIG MONEY.

14:00.240 --> 14:02.572
I'M HOPING YOUR INVOLVEMENT
WILL CONVINCE MediVolt

14:02.572 --> 14:04.474
TO DO ANOTHER ROUND
OF FUNDING.

14:05.976 --> 14:07.117
READ IT.

14:10.480 --> 14:12.052
Kate:
CHECK THIS OUT.

14:12.052 --> 14:14.454
THIS IS SECURITY FOOTAGE
FROM DR. VETTER'S GARAGE.

14:22.492 --> 14:25.865
HIS NAME IS
DR. ARTHUR SINGH,

14:25.865 --> 14:27.998
ENGINEER AT OsciDyne.

14:27.998 --> 14:30.901
AND MAYBE HE ENGINEERED
A MURDER.

14:36.907 --> 14:38.648
Singh: GO TO HELL.

14:38.648 --> 14:40.911
I DIDN'T KILL ANYONE.

14:40.911 --> 14:43.954
Kate:
BUT YOU DID ASSAULT DR. VETTER
IN HIS GARAGE YESTERDAY.

14:43.954 --> 14:46.156
HE FILED A COMPLAINT
WITH THE FDA.

14:46.156 --> 14:48.188
IT WAS MY RIGHT TO TELL HIM
HE WAS MISTAKEN.

14:48.188 --> 14:50.160
YOU EVER HEAR OF THE PHONE,
ARTIE?

14:50.160 --> 14:52.192
I SPENT THREE YEARS,
NIGHT AND DAY,

14:52.192 --> 14:53.363
WORKING ON THE 5.0.

14:53.363 --> 14:55.325
I WAS SIMPLY DEFENDING
MY CREATION.

14:55.325 --> 14:56.566
PRETTY GOOD LIAR,
AREN'T YOU?

14:56.566 --> 14:59.069
I HAVEN'T LIED ABOUT
ANYTHING.

14:59.069 --> 15:01.531
WHAT ABOUT YOUR CRIMINAL RECORD
IN INDIA?

15:01.531 --> 15:03.573
GOT THIS FROM MY FRIENDS
OVER AT I.C.E.

15:03.573 --> 15:06.937
THEY DISCOVERED THAT YOU'D
BEEN CHARGED WITH ASSAULT

15:06.937 --> 15:09.339
FOR BASHING A COWORKER
OVER THE HEAD.

15:09.339 --> 15:11.341
AND THEY REALIZED
THOSE CHARGES WERE TRUMPED UP.

15:11.341 --> 15:13.443
OTHERWISE, THEY NEVER
WOULD HAVE APPROVED MY VISA.

15:13.443 --> 15:16.486
OKAY, SO, I.C.E. GAVE YOU
A PASS, BUT NOT ME.

15:16.486 --> 15:17.948
THIS IS OUTRAGEOUS.

15:17.948 --> 15:19.449
YOU HAVE ABSOLUTELY NOTHING
ON ME.

15:19.449 --> 15:21.921
WHERE WERE YOU THIS MORNING
BETWEEN 6:00 AND 9:00?

15:21.921 --> 15:24.094
HOME -- ASLEEP.

15:24.094 --> 15:25.025
[ DOOR OPENS ]

15:25.025 --> 15:25.695
[ SIGHS ]

15:27.958 --> 15:29.499
THE GUY'S GUILTY.

15:29.499 --> 15:31.331
THE ONLY QUESTION IS,
DID HE ACT ALONE,

15:31.331 --> 15:32.963
OR DID HE HIRE SOMEONE ELSE
TO DO IT?

15:32.963 --> 15:34.464
I UNDERSTAND WHY
HE'D WANT TO GET RID OF VETTER,

15:34.464 --> 15:35.565
BUT WHY THE WIFE?

15:35.565 --> 15:37.367
SHE WAS A WITNESS.
YEAH, MAYBE.

15:37.367 --> 15:39.109
BUT WE DON'T HAVE ANYTHING
TO HOLD SINGH ON.

15:39.109 --> 15:40.971
WE GOT TO CUT HIM LOOSE.
NO WAY.

15:40.971 --> 15:43.343
AN INDIAN NATIONAL?
THE GUY'S A FLIGHT RISK.

15:43.343 --> 15:45.375
I'LL GET
A MATERIAL-WITNESS WARRANT.

15:45.375 --> 15:46.646
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

15:46.646 --> 15:48.118
WHENEVER I ASK YOU
FOR ONE OF THOSE,

15:48.118 --> 15:49.579
YOU TELL ME
I HAVE TO WORK THE CASE

15:49.579 --> 15:51.121
UNTIL THERE'S
AN ACTUAL CHARGE.

15:51.121 --> 15:52.452
WHY IS IT OKAY NOW?

15:52.452 --> 15:54.684
BECAUSE HIS STORY IS WEAK,
HE'S GOT NO ALIBI,

15:54.684 --> 15:56.686
AND ON TOP OF THAT,
HE'S A DICK.

16:01.261 --> 16:03.663
DR. BOWEN
IS TRYING TO HELP PEOPLE.

16:03.663 --> 16:07.397
WHY CAN'T YOU BE MORE
OPEN-MINDED ABOUT HIS DBS TRIAL?

16:07.397 --> 16:09.399
BECAUSE HIS TRIAL
IS UNDERWRITTEN

16:09.399 --> 16:11.671
BY A SOULLESS,
PROFIT-DRIVEN CORPORATION.

16:11.671 --> 16:14.374
REMEMBER THE STUDY THAT COMPARED
CORPORATIONS TO PSYCHOPATHS?

16:14.374 --> 16:16.276
HE SAID SOME OF THEM
BEHAVED IDENTICALLY.

16:16.276 --> 16:17.377
EXACTLY.

16:17.377 --> 16:18.648
WELL, UNLESS
YOU'RE SUGGESTING

16:18.648 --> 16:20.050
THAT I GO TO WORK
WITH A PSYCHOPATH.

16:20.050 --> 16:23.283
OH, DANIEL,
GET OFF YOUR HIGH HORSE.

16:23.283 --> 16:26.256
WHAT ARE YOU
REALLY WORRIED ABOUT --

16:26.256 --> 16:28.018
CORPORATE-FUNDED RESEARCH

16:28.018 --> 16:30.120
OR THAT THIS STUDY
COULD LEAD TO A CURE,

16:30.120 --> 16:32.492
AND THEN YOU WOULDN'T HAVE
AN EXCUSE FOR BEING SICK?
THAT IS PREPOSTEROUS.

16:32.492 --> 16:34.364
AND YOU KNOW WHAT?

16:34.364 --> 16:36.596
E-EVEN IF IT DID
WORK, NO ONE IS PUTTING
ELECTRODES IN MY BRAIN.

16:36.596 --> 16:38.228
Max: HEY, DOC.

16:38.228 --> 16:39.499
YOU GOT A MINUTE?

16:39.499 --> 16:42.001
I THOUGHT THIS MIGHT BE
A GOOD TIME

16:42.001 --> 16:44.574
FOR YOU TO GET TO KNOW EVA
A LITTLE BIT.

16:44.574 --> 16:46.436
NICE TO MEET YOU...
AGAIN.

16:46.436 --> 16:49.539
DOC, EVA'S GOT
AN AMAZING STORY.

16:49.539 --> 16:51.711
SHE MOVED HERE FROM BRAZIL
WITH HER FAMILY.

16:51.711 --> 16:54.444
SHE WAS 11, AND SHE HAD NEVER
SPOKEN ENGLISH BEFORE.

16:54.444 --> 16:56.246
BUT BY THE TIME
SHE GRADUATED HIGH SCHOOL,

16:56.246 --> 16:58.248
SHE WAS AT THE TOP
OF HER CLASS.

16:58.248 --> 17:00.050
NOW SHE RUNS
HER OWN SALON.

17:00.050 --> 17:01.491
I THINK
ALL THAT EVA NEEDS NOW

17:01.491 --> 17:03.553
IS A DEGREE
FROM THE EXTENSION PROGRAM,

17:03.553 --> 17:06.126
AND SHE'S A PERFECT CANDIDATE
FOR A SCHOLARSHIP.

17:06.126 --> 17:07.257
[ SIGHS ]

17:07.257 --> 17:09.399
WHAT ARE YOU INTERESTED
IN STUDYING?

17:09.399 --> 17:11.361
I DIDN'T THINK
THIS WAS GONNA BE AN INTERVIEW.

17:11.361 --> 17:13.133
OH, WELL,
SINCE DR. PIERCE IS SO BUSY,

17:13.133 --> 17:14.434
I FIGURED THAT THIS --

17:14.434 --> 17:16.206
I REALLY APPRECIATE
YOUR TIME, DR. PIERCE.

17:16.206 --> 17:17.567
PLEASE STOP BY THE SALON
SOME DAY.

17:17.567 --> 17:19.139
I'LL GIVE YOU
A FREE HAIRCUT.

17:19.139 --> 17:21.040
OH, NO, NO, NO.
I-I DON'T DO SALONS.

17:21.040 --> 17:24.214
YOU KNOW, THE TOXIC CHEMICALS
AND -- AND THE HAIR DYES

17:24.214 --> 17:26.746
AND THOSE COMBS
IN THE STRANGE BLUE FLUID.

17:26.746 --> 17:29.249
OKAY. WELL...

17:29.249 --> 17:31.451
I BETTER GO.

17:33.553 --> 17:35.555
THANKS A LOT, DOC.

17:35.555 --> 17:37.827
WELL, THAT WASN'T
VERY NICE, DANIEL.

17:39.629 --> 17:41.161
WHO ARE YOU?

17:41.161 --> 17:43.833
GEEZ, I THOUGHT
YOU'D RECOGNIZE ME.

17:43.833 --> 17:45.495
I'M DAN.

17:45.495 --> 17:47.767
GREAT.

17:47.767 --> 17:50.440
I'M HALLUCINATING MYSELF.

17:50.440 --> 17:52.372
OH, I'M NOT EXACTLY YOU.

17:52.372 --> 17:53.343
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

17:53.343 --> 17:55.105
FOR STARTERS, I'M HAPPY...

17:55.105 --> 17:58.478
COMFORTABLE IN MY OWN SKIN,
CONSIDERATE, OPEN-MINDED.

17:58.478 --> 18:00.650
I AM VERY OPEN-MINDED.

18:00.650 --> 18:02.682
PLEASE.
I KNOW YOU.

18:02.682 --> 18:04.514
I USED TO BE YOU --

18:04.514 --> 18:07.487
BURIED IN HEADPHONES
HALF THE DAY,

18:07.487 --> 18:10.460
OBSESSED WITH PUZZLES,
PARANOID...

18:10.460 --> 18:12.162
ALONE.

18:12.162 --> 18:15.665
BUT THIS...
CHANGED EVERYTHING.

18:15.665 --> 18:17.497
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

18:17.497 --> 18:20.430
I TOLD YOU --
I HAVE AN OPEN MIND.

18:22.802 --> 18:25.275
THE FUTURE IS NOW,
MY FRIEND.

18:25.275 --> 18:28.338
NO MORE HALLUCINATIONS.
NO MORE DELUSIONS.

18:28.338 --> 18:30.410
OH, WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

18:30.410 --> 18:32.782
TREATING SCHIZOPHRENIA WITH DBS
IS JUST A THEORY.

18:32.782 --> 18:34.214
YOU ARE NOT REAL,

18:34.214 --> 18:35.145
AND NEITHER IS
YOUR BRAIN IMPLANT.

18:35.145 --> 18:36.716
OH, YOU GOT ME THERE.

18:36.716 --> 18:40.119
MY DBS IS JUST A HALLUCINATION,
BUT SUSAN VETTER'S...

18:41.421 --> 18:42.822
...IS REAL.

18:42.822 --> 18:45.155
SO WHAT?

18:45.155 --> 18:47.427
SO YOU CAN USE IT.

18:48.898 --> 18:51.561
I COULD WAKE HER UP.

18:58.838 --> 19:00.840
W-WE'RE LUCKY.

19:00.840 --> 19:03.713
SUSAN VETTER IS IN A MINIMALLY
CONSCIOUS STATE, NOT A COMA.

19:03.713 --> 19:05.275
AND BECAUSE SHE HAS
ESSENTIAL TREMOR,

19:05.275 --> 19:08.178
HER DBS ELECTRODES
ARE IN THE SUBTHALAMIC AREA.

19:08.178 --> 19:10.820
IF YOU COULD RETREAT THEM
TO THE THALAMUS --

19:10.820 --> 19:13.152
WE MAY BE ABLE TO
JOLT HER AWAKE.
EXACTLY.

19:13.152 --> 19:14.584
THAT'S BRILLIANT, PIERCE.

19:14.584 --> 19:17.557
BUT AS FAR AS I KNOW,
IT'S NEVER BEEN DONE BEFORE.

19:17.557 --> 19:19.158
I'M GONNA NEED YOU THERE.

19:19.158 --> 19:20.790
OH, I-I DON'T DO
OPERATING ROOMS.

19:20.790 --> 19:22.832
I KNOW ABOUT
YOUR DIAGNOSIS.

19:22.832 --> 19:25.395
IT'S ONE OF THE REASONS
I ASKED YOU TO HELP
ME WITH MY STUDY.

19:25.395 --> 19:26.696
THEN YOU KNOW
WHY I CAN'T BE THERE.

19:26.696 --> 19:28.738
I AM NOT ASKING YOU
TO HOLD A SCALPEL.

19:28.738 --> 19:32.302
BUT I NEED YOU
TO WATCH THE MONITOR,

19:32.302 --> 19:36.276
HELP ME TARGET
THE RIGHT AREA OF THE BRAIN.

19:36.276 --> 19:40.480
I CAN'T ALWAYS BE CONFIDENT
IN WHAT I'M SEEING.

19:40.480 --> 19:43.453
HAS YOUR ILLNESS STOPPED YOU
FROM BEING AN EFFECTIVE TEACHER

19:43.453 --> 19:47.757
OR HELPING THE FBI
OR WRITING BOOKS?

19:47.757 --> 19:49.519
[ SIGHS ]

19:49.519 --> 19:52.622
WE'RE GONNA NEED HER SON'S
PERMISSION FOR THE SURGERY.

19:58.898 --> 20:00.630
I-I DON'T KNOW.

20:00.630 --> 20:03.373
CAN'T WE WAIT AND SEE
IF SHE'LL WAKE UP ON HER OWN?

20:03.373 --> 20:05.875
YOU MOTHER'S BRAIN ACTIVITY
IS STEADILY DECLINING.

20:05.875 --> 20:08.578
THIS MAY BE THE BEST CHANCE
WE HAVE TO REVIVE HER.

20:08.578 --> 20:10.610
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

20:10.610 --> 20:12.982
IAN, I'M TESS WILLIAMS.
I WORK WITH OsciDyne.

20:12.982 --> 20:15.915
THE HOSPITAL ALERTED US
TO DR. BOWEN'S RISKY PROPOSAL.

20:15.915 --> 20:19.519
NOW, DO YOU UNDERSTAND THAT THIS
IS NOT AN FDA-APPROVED USAGE?

20:21.651 --> 20:23.653
YOU DIDN'T TELL ME THAT.

20:23.653 --> 20:24.954
WE WOULD BE OPERATING

20:24.954 --> 20:26.656
UNDER AN EMERGENCY EXEMPTION
TO FDA RULES.

20:26.656 --> 20:27.827
IT'S NOT UNCOMMON.

20:27.827 --> 20:29.399
IT DOESN'T MAKE IT
LESS RISKY.

20:29.399 --> 20:31.261
IT'S MY LEGAL OBLIGATION
TO TELL YOU

20:31.261 --> 20:33.633
THAT OsciDyne CAN'T
BE HELD LIABLE FOR THE OUTCOME.

20:33.633 --> 20:36.366
THIS IS NOT ABOUT LIABILITY.
THIS IS ABOUT A WOMAN'S LIFE.

20:37.807 --> 20:38.668
LOOK AT HER.

20:41.271 --> 20:43.513
IF THAT WAS YOUR MOTHER,
WHAT WOULD YOU DO?

20:43.513 --> 20:45.945
I'D WANT TO KNOW ALL THE FACTS
BEFORE I MADE ANY DECISION.

20:45.945 --> 20:48.648
HERE'S MY CARD.

20:48.648 --> 20:49.819
OKAY?

20:49.819 --> 20:50.780
FEEL FREE TO CALL ME.

21:05.264 --> 21:06.566
GO FOR IT.

21:13.803 --> 21:15.775
HOW WE DOING,
DR. PIERCE?

21:15.775 --> 21:17.777
[ SIGHS ]
W-WE'RE CLOSE.

21:17.777 --> 21:20.049
ONE MILLIMETER HIGHER.

21:20.049 --> 21:22.582
STOP THERE.

21:22.582 --> 21:23.913
[ SIGHS ]

21:23.913 --> 21:25.315
I THINK --
I THINK THAT'S YOUR BEST BET.

21:25.315 --> 21:26.456
CONTROLLER.

21:29.989 --> 21:30.990
COME ON, SUSAN.

21:30.990 --> 21:32.822
WAKE UP.

21:32.822 --> 21:34.494
[ BEEPING ]

21:35.865 --> 21:38.498
LET'S TRY
A HIGHER PULSE WIDTH.

21:42.031 --> 21:44.874
IT'S NOT WORKING,
HUH?

21:44.874 --> 21:46.005
Go away.

21:46.005 --> 21:47.337
HER E.E.G. IS DROPPING.

21:47.337 --> 21:48.838
MAYBE YOU SHOULD LET ME
HANDLE THIS.

21:48.838 --> 21:50.309
I MEAN, I'M NOT SICK.

21:50.309 --> 21:51.611
Hey, this whole thing
was your idea!

21:51.611 --> 21:53.042
WHAT?
NOTHING.

21:53.042 --> 21:54.884
YOU OKAY?

21:54.884 --> 21:56.616
Dan: NO, HE'S NOT.

21:56.616 --> 21:58.618
HE'S AN UNTREATED
SCHIZOPHRENIC.

21:58.618 --> 21:59.619
AND WHAT'S WORSE,

21:59.619 --> 22:01.351
HE'S INCOMPETENT.

22:01.351 --> 22:04.454
WE'RE LOSING HER.
WE NEED TO END THE SURGERY.

22:04.454 --> 22:06.426
COME ON, PAL.
YOU CAN DO THIS.

22:06.426 --> 22:07.757
NO, NO, WAIT, WAIT.

22:07.757 --> 22:09.328
UH...

22:09.328 --> 22:10.530
TRY ONE MORE PLACEMENT.

22:10.530 --> 22:11.701
ONE MILLIMETER HIGHER

22:11.701 --> 22:14.464
TO THE THALAMIC
RETICULAR NUCLEUS.

22:14.464 --> 22:15.905
[ BEEPING ]

22:16.936 --> 22:18.968
[ BREATHING DEEPLY ]

22:18.968 --> 22:20.039
HER EYES ARE MOVING.

22:20.039 --> 22:22.372
INCREASE PULSE TRAIN
TO 30 HERTZ.

22:24.113 --> 22:26.916
SUSAN, CAN YOU HEAR ME?

22:26.916 --> 22:28.918
YES.

22:30.650 --> 22:32.722
WELL DONE.

22:33.923 --> 22:35.124
Dan: ATTABOY.

22:41.391 --> 22:44.964
CAN YOU TELL ME YOUR NAME
AND YOUR DATE OF BIRTH?

22:44.964 --> 22:46.666
SUSAN EVELYN VETTER.

22:46.666 --> 22:47.867
APRIL 5, 1971.

22:47.867 --> 22:49.669
YOUR CURRENT ADDRESS?

22:49.669 --> 22:52.502
183 KIRTLAND STREET,
ARDEN, ILLINOIS.

22:52.502 --> 22:54.544
WHAT IS THE LAST THING
YOU REMEMBER

22:54.544 --> 22:56.546
BEFORE WAKING UP
IN THE HOSPITAL?

22:56.546 --> 22:59.649
I-I WAS AT HOME
IN MY KITCHEN.

22:59.649 --> 23:00.880
OKAY.

23:00.880 --> 23:03.052
THIS MIGHT BE HARD
FOR YOU, BUT...

23:03.052 --> 23:04.654
I NEED YOU TO TELL ME

23:04.654 --> 23:07.557
WHAT HAPPENED IN YOUR HOUSE
THAT MORNING.

23:07.557 --> 23:11.060
RANDALL HAD JUST LEFT
FOR WORK.

23:11.060 --> 23:15.725
I WAS AT THE SINK
WASHING THE DISHES WHEN...

23:15.725 --> 23:20.970
OH, FOR SOME REASON,
MY TREMOR STARTED TO GET WORSE.

23:20.970 --> 23:23.102
[ PLATE SHATTERS ]

23:23.102 --> 23:25.435
[ CUP SHATTERS ]

23:25.435 --> 23:28.107
I-IT FELT LIKE
MY DBS WAS BACK ON.

23:28.107 --> 23:30.910
BUT THAT DIDN'T --
IT DIDN'T MAKE ANY SENSE.

23:30.910 --> 23:32.982
MY HUSBAND HAD TURNED IT OFF
THE NIGHT BEFORE.

23:32.982 --> 23:35.184
BECAUSE OF WHAT HAPPENED
TO SARIO?

23:35.184 --> 23:36.586
YEAH.

23:36.586 --> 23:39.489
I STARTED TO FEEL
REALLY...ANGRY

23:39.489 --> 23:43.893
THAT RANDALL HAD MADE
SOME KIND OF MISTAKE, AND...

23:43.893 --> 23:48.427
AND THEN, HE, UH...
HE WALKED BACK INTO THE KITCHEN.

23:48.427 --> 23:50.129
[ SUSAN STAMMERING ]

23:50.129 --> 23:52.832
I THOUGHT YOU TURNED
MY DBS OFF.

23:52.832 --> 23:54.133
SUSAN, CALM DOWN.

23:54.133 --> 23:56.566
DON'T TELL ME
TO CALM DOWN!

23:58.137 --> 23:59.969
AFTER THAT,
I-I DON'T REMEMBER ANYTHING.

23:59.969 --> 24:01.010
I MUST HAVE BLACKED OUT.

24:02.612 --> 24:05.545
WHERE IS RANDALL?

24:07.216 --> 24:08.548
IS HE ALL RIGHT?

24:10.019 --> 24:11.651
I'M SORRY, SUSAN.

24:13.723 --> 24:16.185
OH, MY GOD.

24:16.185 --> 24:19.188
DID I KILL MY HUSBAND?

24:22.031 --> 24:23.833
OH, MY GOD.

24:23.833 --> 24:28.167
[ SOBBING ]

24:32.872 --> 24:34.744
HIS WIFE KILLED HIM?

24:34.744 --> 24:36.205
THAT DOESN'T MAKE
ANY SENSE.

24:36.205 --> 24:38.708
SHE WAS ALMOST DEAD
BY THE TIME THE COPS GOT THERE.

24:38.708 --> 24:39.909
BUT BEFORE
SHE COLLAPSED,

24:39.909 --> 24:41.511
SHE WAS IN
A HIGHLY AGITATED STATE.

24:41.511 --> 24:42.882
SO, FIRST,
SHE SHOVES HER HUSBAND,

24:42.882 --> 24:44.153
AND THEN
SHE HAS THE SEIZURE.

24:44.153 --> 24:45.715
WHOA, WHOA, WAIT.

24:45.715 --> 24:47.517
YOU SAID THAT SARIO WAS
IN A HIGHLY AGITATED STATE

24:47.517 --> 24:48.988
BEFORE HIS SEIZURE,
TOO, RIGHT?

24:48.988 --> 24:50.590
RIGHT, RIGHT.

24:50.590 --> 24:52.662
SO, I'M GUESSING THAT SUSAN'S
DBS LEVELS SURGED

24:52.662 --> 24:53.923
JUST LIKE SARIO'S.

24:53.923 --> 24:55.525
ANOTHER NAIL
IN OsciDyne's COFFIN.

24:55.525 --> 24:58.798
WHEN SUSAN GOT TO THE HOSPITAL,
HER DBS WAS OFF.

24:58.798 --> 25:02.632
SO, MAYBE IT -- IT WAS SABOTAGE
LIKE SINGH SUGGESTED.

25:02.632 --> 25:04.033
HANG ON A SECOND.

25:04.033 --> 25:06.536
YOU'RE SAYING THAT SOMEBODY
JACKED UP HER DBS LEVELS

25:06.536 --> 25:07.937
AND THEN TURNED IT BACK OFF?

25:07.937 --> 25:09.278
WHY WOULD ANYONE DO THAT?

25:09.278 --> 25:11.510
I DON'T KNOW,
B-B-BUT TO DO IT,

25:11.510 --> 25:13.082
THEY'D -- THEY'D HAVE TO KNOW
HER WIRELESS CODE,

25:13.082 --> 25:14.914
AND THEY WOULD HAVE TO BE
CLOSE BY.

25:14.914 --> 25:17.787
LOOK, I KNOW IT SOUNDS CRAZY,
BUT VETTER WAS RIGHT THERE,

25:17.787 --> 25:19.719
AND HE DEFINITELY
HAD HER CODE.

25:19.719 --> 25:21.691
OF COURSE.
THE DEAD GUY DID IT.

25:21.691 --> 25:23.893
WELL, EXCUSE ME,
BUT IN MY EXPERIENCE,

25:23.893 --> 25:25.695
THE HUSBAND'S
USUALLY THE KILLER,

25:25.695 --> 25:27.296
NOT THE BIG BIOTECH FIRM.
REALLY?

25:27.296 --> 25:32.061
THEN EXPLAIN HOW HE TURNED OFF
HER DBS AFTER HE WAS DEAD.

25:32.061 --> 25:33.863
MAYBE HE ZAPPED HER,

25:33.863 --> 25:36.966
BUT THEN HE TALKED TO YOU ON
THE PHONE, CHANGED HIS MIND,

25:36.966 --> 25:38.968
WENT BACK IN THE HOUSE,
TURNED HER DBS OFF.

25:38.968 --> 25:42.241
BUT BY THEN, IT WAS TOO LATE.
SHE WAS ALREADY IN A RAGE.

25:42.241 --> 25:43.743
IT MAKES SENSE.

25:43.743 --> 25:45.244
I MEAN,
A GUY WANTS TO KILL HIS WIFE,

25:45.244 --> 25:46.976
HE KNOWS HE CAN DO IT
BY MAXING OUT HER DBS LEVEL.

25:46.976 --> 25:49.919
AND -- AND HE KNOWS ABOUT
THE SERIES OF MALFUNCTIONS

25:49.919 --> 25:51.180
WITH -- WITH HER MODEL.

25:51.180 --> 25:52.582
IT'S A PERFECT COVER.

25:52.582 --> 25:54.053
SO, WHEN SHE DIES,

25:54.053 --> 25:56.085
HE CLAIMS IT WAS JUST
ANOTHER DEFECTIVE DEVICE.

25:56.085 --> 25:58.928
IT'S SICK, BUT IT'S
KIND OF BRILLIANT.

25:58.928 --> 26:00.259
WHATEVER HAPPENED,

26:00.259 --> 26:02.231
SUSAN ADMITTED
THAT SHE PUSHED HIM,

26:02.231 --> 26:04.033
SO YOU GOT TO
CUT SINGH LOOSE.

26:07.266 --> 26:08.998
WELL, WE'RE STILL
GOING AFTER OsciDyne

26:08.998 --> 26:10.269
FOR THE EIGHT OTHER
FAILURES.

26:10.269 --> 26:12.571
DAMN RIGHT.

26:14.003 --> 26:15.605
SO WHAT NOW?
[ SIGHS ]

26:15.605 --> 26:17.877
WE CAN'T GET A CONFESSION
OUT OF A DEAD MAN.

26:17.877 --> 26:20.579
WELL, WE CAN STILL PROVE
THAT THE DBS WAS MANIPULATED.

26:20.579 --> 26:22.151
I'LL GET FLECKNER IN CYBER
ON IT.

26:22.151 --> 26:26.255
IN THE MEANTIME,
LET'S TRY TO ESTABLISH A MOTIVE.

26:26.255 --> 26:29.218
TELL ME ABOUT
YOUR PARENTS' RELATIONSHIP.

26:29.218 --> 26:31.120
YOU'RE ASKING ME THAT NOW?

26:31.120 --> 26:35.264
LISTEN, IAN, YOUR MOTHER HAS
ADMITTED TO KILLING YOUR FATHER.

26:35.264 --> 26:38.097
YOU'RE SERIOUSLY TELLING ME
SHE COULD GO TO JAIL?

26:39.298 --> 26:40.970
LISTEN, EVEN IF
SHE DIDN'T MEAN TO DO IT,

26:40.970 --> 26:44.103
SHE COULD STILL BE FACING
MANSLAUGHTER CHARGES.

26:47.206 --> 26:49.909
THEIR MARRIAGE
WASN'T PERFECT.

26:49.909 --> 26:51.641
"NOT PERFECT" HOW?

26:51.641 --> 26:54.143
WHEN MY MOM'S TREMORS
GOT BAD,

26:54.143 --> 26:57.186
MY DAD GOT A, UH...
A WANDERING EYE.

26:57.186 --> 26:58.918
YOU MEAN A GIRLFRIEND?

26:58.918 --> 27:01.891
MOM THOUGHT HE WAS HAVING
AN AFFAIR WITH HIS SECRETARY.

27:03.122 --> 27:05.795
Gabby:
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

27:05.795 --> 27:07.997
I MEAN,
HE FLIRTED A LITTLE BIT.

27:07.997 --> 27:09.929
WE HAD DRINKS AFTER WORK
A FEW TIMES,

27:09.929 --> 27:11.360
BUT I NEVER
SLEPT WITH HIM.

27:12.962 --> 27:14.333
FLECKNER.

27:14.333 --> 27:15.805
PIERCE.

27:15.805 --> 27:17.136
Gabby:
BUT TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH,

27:17.136 --> 27:18.838
I THOUGHT HE WAS HAVING
AN AFFAIR, TOO.

27:18.838 --> 27:22.141
SOMETIMES HE WOULD SPEAK
ON THE PHONE IN WHISPERS,

27:22.141 --> 27:25.675
AND OTHER TIMES, HE'D DISAPPEAR
FOR HOURS AT LUNCH.

27:25.675 --> 27:28.247
MORETTI'S WASTING HER TIME.

27:28.247 --> 27:29.949
[ DOOR OPENS ]

27:29.949 --> 27:32.021
I FOUND SOMETHING.

27:32.021 --> 27:33.152
Daniel: A CELLPHONE?

27:33.152 --> 27:34.083
AN MP3 PLAYER.

27:34.083 --> 27:35.685
IT DOESN'T MAKE PHONE CALLS,

27:35.685 --> 27:37.927
BUT IT DOES
JUST ABOUT EVERYTHING ELSE.

27:37.927 --> 27:39.428
THE COPS BAGGED IT
FROM THE KITCHEN COUNTER.

27:39.428 --> 27:42.361
THIS IS THE OsciDyne 5.0
SOFTWARE.

27:42.361 --> 27:45.094
IT WAS THE LAST PROGRAM
RUN ON THE DEVICE,

27:45.094 --> 27:49.098
AND IT WAS SYNCED WITH
SUSAN VETTER'S DBS ACCESS CODE.

27:49.098 --> 27:50.770
GREAT.

27:50.770 --> 27:52.371
NOW THEY CAN USE CELLPHONES
TO TAP INTO OUR BRAINS.

27:52.371 --> 27:55.004
YEAH, IT'S PRETTY COOL, RIGHT?
CHECK THIS OUT.

27:56.445 --> 27:58.447
I SCANNED
THE MP3's MEMORY CARD

27:58.447 --> 28:01.711
AND FOUND THE SYNC CODES
FOR EVERY ONE OF THE FAILURES

28:01.711 --> 28:03.813
YOU GUYS HAVE BEEN
INVESTIGATING.

28:03.813 --> 28:05.084
AND GUESS WHAT --

28:05.084 --> 28:06.385
THEY WERE ALL INTENTIONAL.

28:06.385 --> 28:08.257
SOMEBODY'S
BEEN USING THIS PUPPY

28:08.257 --> 28:11.060
TO TRAVEL AROUND THE COUNTRY
ZAPPING PEOPLE'S BRAINS.

28:11.060 --> 28:13.222
SO, THERE WERE NEVER
ANY MALFUNCTIONS?
NOPE.

28:13.222 --> 28:14.693
LOOKS LIKE VETTER
DID THEM ALL

28:14.693 --> 28:15.995
TO MAKE HIS WIFE'S MURDER

28:15.995 --> 28:17.466
LOOK LIKE PART OF A SERIES
OF PRODUCT FAILURES.

28:17.466 --> 28:18.998
Kate: WELL, I'LL CHECK
HIS TRAVEL RECORDS,

28:18.998 --> 28:21.030
BUT IF WE CAN PUT HIM
AT ANY OF THESE LOCATIONS,

28:21.030 --> 28:22.101
WE'VE GOT OUR GUY.

28:22.101 --> 28:23.702
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

28:23.702 --> 28:26.736
THIS WHOLE THING
WAS JUST A RUN-OF-THE-MILL,

28:26.736 --> 28:28.137
DOMESTIC-MURDER PLOT?

28:28.137 --> 28:29.408
[ CHUCKLES ]
POOR DONNIE.

28:29.408 --> 28:31.110
NOT GONNA GET HIS NAME
IN THE PAPER.

28:32.211 --> 28:34.283
THAT'S NOT
WHAT THIS WAS ABOUT.

28:40.890 --> 28:42.451
TV Announcer:
WE'LL BE RIGHT BACK

28:42.451 --> 28:44.723
WITH OUR HALF-TIME ANALYSIS
RIGHT AFTER...

28:44.723 --> 28:46.756
YOU COULDN'T HAVE GOTTEN
ONE LOUSY HAIRCUT?

28:46.756 --> 28:48.027
EXCUSE ME?

28:48.027 --> 28:50.099
EVA JUST BROKE UP WITH ME --
BY TEXT.

28:50.099 --> 28:51.360
WHAT, YOU'RE BLAMING ME?

28:51.360 --> 28:52.932
NO, I'M NOT BLAMING YOU.

28:52.932 --> 28:55.104
[ SIGHS ] I JUST WISH
I KNEW WHAT I DID WRONG.

28:55.104 --> 28:56.165
WELL, THAT'S OBVIOUS.

28:56.165 --> 28:57.306
YOU PUSHED HER TOO HARD

28:57.306 --> 28:59.138
ON THE WHOLE
EXTENSION-SCHOOL THING.

28:59.138 --> 29:02.041
YOU PROBABLY MADE HER FEEL LIKE
SHE'S NOT SMART ENOUGH FOR YOU.

29:02.041 --> 29:04.413
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

29:04.413 --> 29:05.875
[ SIGHS ]

29:05.875 --> 29:08.177
OF COURSE, DOC.
I'D LOVE TO GET IT.

29:08.177 --> 29:09.448
BE HAPPY TO.

29:09.448 --> 29:11.951
[ MAN SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY
ON TV ]

29:11.951 --> 29:13.382
[ DOOR OPENS ]

29:13.382 --> 29:14.924
[ SIGHS ]

29:14.924 --> 29:15.885
OH.

29:15.885 --> 29:17.226
Max:
HEY, UH...DOC?

29:17.226 --> 29:20.790
OH, IT'S ALL RIGHT.
IT'S ALL RIGHT, LEWICKI.

29:20.790 --> 29:23.332
OH, YOU'RE WATCHING
THE BULLS.

29:23.332 --> 29:24.463
WHO'S WINNING?

29:24.463 --> 29:27.336
CLIPPERS ARE UP BY 10
AT THE HALF.

29:27.336 --> 29:29.198
[ SIGHS ]
BASTARDS.

29:29.198 --> 29:30.369
MNH-MNH.

29:30.369 --> 29:32.001
W-WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE,
DONNIE?

29:32.001 --> 29:36.345
YOU'RE THE BRAIN EXPERT.
READ MY MIND.

29:36.345 --> 29:38.077
FORTUNATELY, I CAN'T.

29:38.077 --> 29:39.809
OKAY, I'LL TELL YOU.

29:39.809 --> 29:41.851
I'M BUMMED.
[ SIGHS ]

29:41.851 --> 29:45.054
I WANTED THE DBS THING
TO BE DEFECTIVE.

29:45.054 --> 29:47.416
YOU WANTED IT.
WHY?

29:47.416 --> 29:49.819
YOU EVER HEAR OF LEXOMYCIN?
YEAH.

29:49.819 --> 29:52.091
IT WAS AN ANTIBIOTIC
LINKED TO HEART PROBLEMS.

29:52.091 --> 29:53.422
BINGO.

29:53.422 --> 29:55.825
WELL, WHEN I FIRST STARTED
AT THE D.O.J.,

29:55.825 --> 29:59.098
MY JOB WAS TO PICK WHICH CASES
TO PASS UP TO MY BOSS.

29:59.098 --> 30:01.871
AND ONE DAY,
LEXOMYCIN LANDED ON MY DESK.

30:01.871 --> 30:03.973
AND YOU KNOW WHAT I DID?
WHAT?

30:03.973 --> 30:05.534
NOTHING.

30:05.534 --> 30:09.808
I THOUGHT IT LOOKED LAME,
AND I WANTED TO LOOK COOL, SO...

30:09.808 --> 30:14.013
I GAVE MY BOSS THIS
ORGANIZED-CRIME THING INSTEAD.

30:14.013 --> 30:15.945
I MEAN, WHAT'S SEXIER

30:15.945 --> 30:19.318
THAN TAKING DOWN
VINCENT CAPECE, RIGHT?

30:19.318 --> 30:22.251
YOU KNOW WHAT HAPPENED
WITH LEXOMYCIN?

30:22.251 --> 30:23.252
40 PEOPLE DIED.

30:23.252 --> 30:24.854
47 PEOPLE DIED.

30:24.854 --> 30:26.225
AND YOU THINK
THAT'S YOUR FAULT?

30:26.225 --> 30:28.157
I KNOW IT'S NOT
ALL MY FAULT.

30:28.157 --> 30:30.529
THE FDA SHOULD HAVE
STOPPED IT SOONER,

30:30.529 --> 30:34.133
AND THE ASSHOLE MANUFACTURER
SHOULD HAVE TESTED IT BETTER,

30:34.133 --> 30:36.265
BUT I SHOULD HAVE
DONE SOMETHING.

30:36.265 --> 30:38.407
SO, LEXOMYCIN'S
WHY YOU TOOK ON OsciDyne.

30:38.407 --> 30:39.438
SEE?

30:39.438 --> 30:41.270
YOU CAN READ MY MIND.

30:41.270 --> 30:44.013
IT'S JUST LIKE KATE SAID.

30:44.013 --> 30:47.276
I ALWAYS HAVE AN ANGLE.
RIGHT?

30:47.276 --> 30:51.350
BUT I DIDN'T WANT MY NAME
IN THE PAPER.

30:51.350 --> 30:52.952
I WANTED...

30:54.853 --> 30:57.026
[ SIGHS ]
I DON'T KNOW.

30:57.026 --> 30:58.958
REDEMPTION?

31:00.429 --> 31:02.061
YEAH.

31:04.964 --> 31:07.967
I'M ALWAYS LOOKING OUT
FOR NUMBER ONE.

31:07.967 --> 31:11.440
AND IT ALWAYS ENDS UP
SCREWING UP OTHER PEOPLE.

31:11.440 --> 31:14.273
THAT'S WHAT I DID
WITH LEXOMYCIN.

31:14.273 --> 31:17.376
AND THAT'S WHAT I DID
WITH MY MARRIAGE.

31:18.447 --> 31:20.549
IT SOUNDS DUMB, BUT...

31:20.549 --> 31:23.452
I THOUGHT THAT
TAKING ON OsciDyne

31:23.452 --> 31:26.515
WOULD PROVE TO KATE
THAT I CHANGED.

31:28.317 --> 31:31.390
I JUST WANTED TO BE THE GUY
SHE THOUGHT SHE MARRIED.

31:34.163 --> 31:37.927
UH...DONNIE...

31:37.927 --> 31:40.229
MAYBE I SHOULD GET...

31:40.229 --> 31:44.073
ONE OF THOSE
DBS THINGIES AND...

31:44.073 --> 31:49.378
IT COULD ZAP ME EVERY TIME
I'M ABOUT TO DO SOMETHING...

31:49.378 --> 31:50.940
STUPID.

31:50.940 --> 31:52.381
DONNIE, ARE --

31:52.381 --> 31:55.284
AT LEAST DONNIE'S TRYING
TO BECOME HIS BETTER SELF.

31:55.284 --> 31:57.947
WHY CAN'T YOU DO THAT, DANIEL?
I DID.

31:57.947 --> 31:59.488
THIS IS RIDICULOUS!

31:59.488 --> 32:01.951
I CAN'T JUST GET A DBS
AND SUDDENLY BE CURED.

32:01.951 --> 32:04.223
BUT YOU COULD DO
A LOT OF OTHER THINGS.

32:04.223 --> 32:06.555
THERE ARE NEW-GENERATION
ANTI-PSYCHOTICS,

32:06.555 --> 32:08.527
AND YOU WON'T USE THOSE,
EITHER.

32:08.527 --> 32:11.500
YOU WON'T EVEN GO TO THERAPY,
WHICH IS A DAMN SHAME,

32:11.500 --> 32:14.333
'CAUSE YOU COULD HAVE
SO MUCH MORE IN YOUR LIFE.

32:14.333 --> 32:17.466
YOU COULD HAVE
WHAT I HAVE...

32:17.466 --> 32:18.968
MY FAMILY.

32:21.610 --> 32:23.572
BEAUTIFUL, AREN'T THEY?

32:23.572 --> 32:25.975
YOU COULD HAVE THIS, TOO...

32:25.975 --> 32:28.978
IF YOU'D JUST TAKE CARE
OF YOURSELF.

32:28.978 --> 32:32.581
I DON'T WANT TO LOOK
AT THAT.

32:32.581 --> 32:34.253
I DON'T BLAME YOU.

32:34.253 --> 32:35.654
IT MUST MAKE YOU FEEL
AWFUL LONELY.

32:35.654 --> 32:40.229
BUT ASK YOURSELF,
WHO ELSE COULDN'T LOOK?

32:40.229 --> 32:41.660
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

32:41.660 --> 32:42.992
PUT THAT AWAY.

32:42.992 --> 32:44.663
YOU'VE BEEN TRYING
TO FIGURE OUT

32:44.663 --> 32:48.097
WHO TURNED OFF
SUSAN VETTER'S DBS.

32:48.097 --> 32:51.200
BUT YOU ALREADY KNOW,
DON'T YOU?

33:02.451 --> 33:04.053
SUSAN VETTER...

33:04.053 --> 33:07.986
WAS TREATED FOR SEIZURES
AND MULTIPLE LACERATIONS,

33:07.986 --> 33:10.459
ALL CAUSED BY BLUNT-FORCE TRAUMA
TO THE BACK OF THE HEAD.

33:10.459 --> 33:12.161
Donnie:
NOW YOU THINK SHE DID IT?

33:12.161 --> 33:13.462
WHEN WE WERE IN THE HOSPITAL,

33:13.462 --> 33:15.324
TESS DIDN'T LOOK AT SUSAN --
NOT ONCE.

33:15.324 --> 33:16.525
SO WHAT?

33:16.525 --> 33:18.067
I DIDN'T WANT
TO LOOK AT HER EITHER.

33:18.067 --> 33:19.728
NO, BUT IF I POINTED AT HER,
YOU WOULD HAVE.

33:19.728 --> 33:21.530
TESS DIDN'T.

33:21.530 --> 33:24.033
IT WAS TOO HARD FOR HER TO LOOK
AT THE WOMAN SHE TRIED TO KILL.

33:24.033 --> 33:25.334
WE'RE GONNA NEED
WAY MORE THAN THAT

33:25.334 --> 33:27.206
TO GET A JURY
PAST REASONABLE DOUBT.

33:27.206 --> 33:28.377
WELL, THERE IS MORE.

33:28.377 --> 33:29.538
VETTER SAID
HE SAW TESS IN MIAMI.

33:29.538 --> 33:31.110
I THINK THEY WERE HAVING
AN AFFAIR.

33:31.110 --> 33:32.211
CIRCUMSTANTIAL.

33:32.211 --> 33:33.412
WHICH IS WHY WE NEED
A CONFESSION.

33:33.412 --> 33:34.743
AND HOW ARE YOU
GONNA GET THAT?

33:34.743 --> 33:37.386
WATCH.

33:37.386 --> 33:39.748
HAVE YOU EVER
SEEN THESE BEFORE, TESS?

33:39.748 --> 33:41.550
[ SIGHS ]
LOOK.

33:41.550 --> 33:43.752
PUT THEM AWAY, PLEASE.
NOT UNTIL YOU ANSWER
MY QUESTIONS.

33:50.399 --> 33:52.030
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO KNOW?

33:55.634 --> 33:57.406
SORRY.

33:57.406 --> 33:58.637
YOU REMEMBER DR. PIERCE.

33:58.637 --> 34:00.769
Daniel:
YES. TESS AND I HAVE MET.

34:00.769 --> 34:03.812
OH...MY.

34:06.245 --> 34:09.378
IT'S TERRIBLE
WHAT HAPPENED TO RANDALL VETTER.

34:09.378 --> 34:12.381
I'M SURE YOU WERE
PRETTY BROKEN UP ABOUT IT.

34:12.381 --> 34:13.782
HE WAS A WONDERFUL MAN.

34:13.782 --> 34:15.084
I LIKED HIM.

34:15.084 --> 34:17.156
YOU LOVED HIM,
DIDN'T YOU?

34:17.156 --> 34:19.228
WHAT?

34:19.228 --> 34:21.130
NO, HE --
IT'S OKAY.

34:21.130 --> 34:23.392
IT MUST BE SO HARD
TO BE THE OTHER WOMAN.

34:23.392 --> 34:25.394
THE FAMILY
GETS ALL THE SYMPATHY.

34:25.394 --> 34:28.137
NOBODY THINKS ABOUT
HOW YOU FEEL.

34:30.399 --> 34:32.801
IF YOU DON'T MIND
MY ASKING...

34:32.801 --> 34:34.373
HOW DID IT START?

34:34.373 --> 34:35.804
I MET HIM
THREE YEARS AGO,

34:35.804 --> 34:38.277
RIGHT AFTER I GOT HIRED
BY OsciDyne.

34:38.277 --> 34:41.680
HE WAS KIND...

34:41.680 --> 34:42.781
AND PATIENT.

34:42.781 --> 34:45.314
I'D NEVER MET
A MAN LIKE HIM.

34:45.314 --> 34:48.587
AND WE BOTH FELT SOMETHING.

34:48.587 --> 34:50.289
THEN YOU SLEPT TOGETHER?

34:50.289 --> 34:52.291
NO.
RANDALL WASN'T LIKE THAT.

34:52.291 --> 34:53.562
BUT AFTER A WHILE,

34:53.562 --> 34:57.426
HIS WIFE SUSAN'S TREMORS
GOT REALLY BAD.

34:57.426 --> 34:58.697
HE STILL LOVED HER,

34:58.697 --> 35:00.669
BUT HE WASN'T
ATTRACTED TO HER ANYMORE.

35:00.669 --> 35:02.871
THAT'S WHEN WE STARTED
SEEING EACH OTHER.

35:02.871 --> 35:06.104
BUT THEN SUSAN GOT DBS,
AND HER TREMORS WENT AWAY.

35:06.104 --> 35:07.436
DID THAT CHANGE THINGS?

35:07.436 --> 35:08.737
YES.

35:08.737 --> 35:11.540
RANDALL STARTED SPENDING
MORE TIME AT HOME.

35:11.540 --> 35:13.312
THAT MUST HAVE HURT.

35:13.312 --> 35:15.214
IT DID.

35:15.214 --> 35:17.846
AND THAT'S WHEN YOU DECIDED TO
DO SOMETHING ABOUT SUSAN VETTER.

35:17.846 --> 35:20.349
Daniel:
WITH SUSAN GONE,

35:20.349 --> 35:22.821
YOU AND RANDALL COULD HAVE
A-A REAL LIFE TOGETHER --
MARRIAGE, MAYBE CHILDREN.

35:22.821 --> 35:25.194
HER DBS WAS THE PERFECT WAY
TO GET RID OF HER.

35:25.194 --> 35:27.496
NO.
BUT YOU DIDN'T WANT RANDALL
TO SUSPECT ANYTHING,

35:27.496 --> 35:29.158
SO YOU CAME UP WITH A PLAN

35:29.158 --> 35:31.760
TO MAKE IT LOOK LIKE
SUSAN'S UNIT WAS DEFECTIVE.

35:31.760 --> 35:34.463
AND BECAUSE OF YOUR JOB, YOU HAD
THE PATIENTS' ACCESS CODES.

35:35.864 --> 35:38.707
TESS, WE FOUND YOUR MP3.

35:38.707 --> 35:40.909
YOUR FINGERPRINTS
ARE ALL OVER IT.

35:45.174 --> 35:47.516
[ SIGHS ]

35:49.918 --> 35:52.481
I ONLY RAISED THEIR SETTINGS
A FEW LEVELS.

35:54.383 --> 35:56.885
JUST ENOUGH
SO THEY'D HAVE SIDE EFFECTS.

35:56.885 --> 36:00.189
BUT THEN YOU MADE THE MISTAKE
OF TARGETING SARIO.

36:00.189 --> 36:05.534
[ MID-TEMPO VIOLIN MUSIC
PLAYING ]

36:05.534 --> 36:07.536
[ OFF-KEY NOTES PLAY ]

36:07.536 --> 36:08.537
[ GRUNTING ]

36:08.537 --> 36:09.868
[ AUDIENCE GASPS ]

36:09.868 --> 36:11.770
Daniel: YOU NEVER THOUGHT
YOUR ATTACK ON HIM

36:11.770 --> 36:13.902
WOULD MAKE THE DOCTOR WANT TO
TAKE OUT SUSAN'S DBS, TOO.

36:13.902 --> 36:15.744
Kate: YOU HAD TO ACT

36:15.744 --> 36:17.476
BECAUSE YOU WEREN'T GONNA GET
ANOTHER CHANCE TO KILL HER.

36:21.650 --> 36:23.712
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES,
ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

36:29.388 --> 36:33.792
Tess: I HAD TO GET CLOSE ENOUGH
TO CONNECT WITH HER UNIT.

36:33.792 --> 36:35.664
ONCE I DID,
I TURNED HER DBS BACK ON,

36:35.664 --> 36:37.466
AND I STARTED TO RAISE
THE LEVELS.

36:39.398 --> 36:42.901
[ PLATE THUNKS ]
I WAS ALMOST FINISHED.

36:42.901 --> 36:43.972
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

36:43.972 --> 36:46.405
BUT THEN RANDALL CAME BACK.

36:46.405 --> 36:48.277
HE WASN'T SUPPOSED TO BE THERE.

36:48.277 --> 36:50.309
I THOUGHT
YOU TURNED MY DBS OFF.

36:50.309 --> 36:51.410
SUSAN, CALM DOWN.

36:51.410 --> 36:53.242
DON'T TELL ME
TO CALM DOWN!

36:53.242 --> 36:54.543
[ THUD ]

36:55.944 --> 36:57.516
[ GRUNTS ]

36:57.516 --> 36:59.918
BUT I HAD TO SEE
IF RANDALL WAS HURT.

36:59.918 --> 37:03.952
AT FIRST, I SAW SUSAN.
IT WAS HORRIBLE.

37:03.952 --> 37:06.325
AND THEN I SAW RANDALL.

37:18.737 --> 37:22.371
[ Crying ] I JUST WANTED RANDALL
FOR MYSELF.

37:27.846 --> 37:30.979
I FORGOT TO TELL YOU --
YOU'RE OUT OF O.J. SORRY.

37:30.979 --> 37:33.952
WELL, YOU PROBABLY NEEDED IT
AFTER LAST NIGHT.

37:33.952 --> 37:35.253
[ CLAPS HANDS ]
YEAH.

37:35.253 --> 37:36.655
[ SIGHS ]

37:36.655 --> 37:38.026
I SHOULDN'T HAVE BARGED IN
ON YOU LIKE THAT.

37:39.488 --> 37:41.660
THANKS FOR NOT THROWING ME OUT
ON MY ASS.

37:43.762 --> 37:46.435
[ SIGHS ]
DO ME A FAVOR?

37:46.435 --> 37:47.796
DON'T TELL KATE.

37:49.468 --> 37:50.599
I WON'T.

37:50.599 --> 37:52.601
MAYBE YOU SHOULD.

37:54.373 --> 37:55.544
[ SIGHS ]

37:55.544 --> 37:57.045
SO, WHO WON THE GAME,
ANYWAY?

37:57.045 --> 37:58.006
WE DID.

37:58.006 --> 38:00.609
DA' BULLS.

38:07.616 --> 38:11.320
DANIEL PIERCE
BUMPING FISTS.

38:11.320 --> 38:12.561
REALLY?

38:12.561 --> 38:14.363
JUST BE CAREFUL
YOU DON'T PICK UP

38:14.363 --> 38:16.525
ANY OF HIS OTHER
JUVENILE HABITS, OKAY?

38:16.525 --> 38:17.896
HE'S NOT THAT BAD.

38:17.896 --> 38:20.699
MAYBE YOU SHOULD CUT HIM
SOME SLACK.

38:26.505 --> 38:30.038
HEY.
THANKS FOR COMING.

38:31.710 --> 38:34.012
I DON'T KNOW WHAT ELSE
THERE IS TO SAY.

38:34.012 --> 38:36.084
YOU DON'T HAVE TO SAY
ANYTHING.

38:36.084 --> 38:38.917
LOOK, I-I KNOW WHY
YOU BROKE UP WITH ME.

38:42.050 --> 38:44.523
YOU THOUGHT I WAS
[SIGHS]

38:44.523 --> 38:47.526
JUDGING YOU BECAUSE
YOU DON'T HAVE A COLLEGE DEGREE.

38:47.526 --> 38:49.858
YOU MADE SUCH A BIG DEAL
ABOUT THE SCHOLARSHIP.

38:49.858 --> 38:51.800
I MEAN,
HOW WAS I SUPPOSED TO FEEL?

38:53.832 --> 38:55.834
WHEN I WAS IN HIGH SCHOOL...

38:55.834 --> 38:58.407
I FELT LIKE
I DIDN'T MEASURE UP.

38:58.407 --> 39:01.810
I WAS A SKINNY, ADOPTED KID
WHO SUCKED AT SPORTS,

39:01.810 --> 39:04.943
AND I HAD A LAST NAME
THAT ENDS WITH "ICKY."

39:04.943 --> 39:08.577
BUT GOING TO COLLEGE,
GETTING A SCHOLARSHIP,

39:08.577 --> 39:12.080
THOSE THINGS MADE ME FEEL
BETTER ABOUT MYSELF.

39:12.080 --> 39:15.554
SO, BECAUSE YOU WERE INSECURE,
YOU THINK I AM, TOO?

39:15.554 --> 39:18.427
I JUST WANTED TO HELP YOU.

39:18.427 --> 39:22.591
HOW ABOUT NEXT TIME,
YOU ASK ME WHAT I WANT?

39:22.591 --> 39:24.593
NEXT TIME?

39:38.547 --> 39:40.449
OKAY,
WANT TO DO THIS?

39:40.449 --> 39:41.149
YOU READY?

39:41.149 --> 39:42.150
LET'S TRY.

40:02.100 --> 40:04.803
[ OFF-KEY NOTES PLAY ]

40:11.980 --> 40:14.613
LET ME TRY
A LOWER PULSE WIDTH.

40:14.613 --> 40:16.485
[ BEEPING ]

40:16.485 --> 40:22.721
[ NOTE PLAYS ]

40:22.721 --> 40:25.994
[ MELODY PLAYS ]

40:35.003 --> 40:40.168
Daniel:
WHY ARE HUMANS CONSTANTLY
STRIVING FOR IMPROVEMENT?

40:40.168 --> 40:44.673
MUCH OF OUR AMBITION IS DRIVEN
BY OUR LARGE PREFRONTAL CORTEX,

40:44.673 --> 40:46.515
WHICH IS WHY
WE'RE IN THIS CLASSROOM

40:46.515 --> 40:48.116
AND NOT IN THE JUNGLE
EATING BANANAS.

40:48.116 --> 40:49.978
[ LAUGHTER ]

40:49.978 --> 40:51.920
EVERY DAY, WE DREAM ABOUT NEW
TECHNOLOGICAL ADVANCEMENTS --

40:51.920 --> 40:55.554
UPGRADED CELLPHONES,
FASTER COMPUTERS,

40:55.554 --> 40:57.956
NEW MEDICAL TECHNIQUES.

40:57.956 --> 41:02.631
SCIENCE SEEMS TO HAVE
UNLIMITED POTENTIAL.

41:02.631 --> 41:07.796
AND MANY OF THESE ADVANCEMENTS
REALLY DO MAKE OUR LIVES BETTER.

41:07.796 --> 41:12.501
BUT SOMETIMES, I THINK,
IN OUR STRIVING FOR IMPROVEMENT,

41:12.501 --> 41:16.204
WE LOSE SIGHT OF SOMETHING
JUST AS IMPORTANT.

41:16.204 --> 41:18.076
MAYBE WE SHOULD TRY TO ACCEPT

41:18.076 --> 41:20.909
WHAT'S ALREADY PRETTY GOOD
ABOUT OURSELVES.

41:25.714 --> 41:28.216
AND NOT EVERYTHING
NEEDS FIXING.

41:28.216 --> 41:32.991
MOZART'S MUSIC IS 200 YEARS OLD.

41:32.991 --> 41:36.565
IT DOESN'T REQUIRE ANY UPGRADE.

41:36.565 --> 41:39.067
IT'S PERFECT JUST THE WAY IT IS.

41:39.067 --> 41:40.769
[ SONG ENDS ]
